fireball.description: Quick cooldown and packs a punch. Good old trusty fireball.

flamestrike.name: Fireboom
flamestrike.description: It's slower than fireball - harder to aim, but does more damage. Takes 0.5 seconds to grow to full damage, so keep a little bit of distance for maximum effect.

firespray.name: Firesplatter
firespray.description: Shoot a stream of fire in a wide arc. Get closer to focus all your damage onto one target.

triplet.name: Trifire
triplet.description: Each bolt of Trifire will add another stack of 2 damage per second to your enemy. There is no limit to the number of stacks, but you must hit them with Trifire at least once every 4 seconds to keep the fire burning.

difire.name: Difire
difire.description: Each bolt of Difire will add another stack of 2.5 damage per second to your enemy. There is no limit to the number of stacks, but you must hit them with Difire at least once every 4 seconds to keep the fire burning.

meteor.description: Send a giant meteor towards your enemies! Nothing stops a meteor.

meteorite.description: Send a little meteorite towards your enemies! Meteorite will split in two if it collides with any other projectiles.

gravity.name: Ensnare
gravity.description: Hold an enemy in place while you unleash your volleys upon them.

effects.title: Silence
effects.text: Your enemy will be unable to cast spells for 0.75 seconds.

effects.title: Recharge
effects.text: If it hits, reduces cooldowns for all your spells except Ensnare by 4 seconds.

whirlwind.name: Freezing Breath
whirlwind.description: A freezing whirlwind to slow your enemies. The whirlwind also catches enemy projectiles.

effects.title: Slow
effects.text: Enemies caught in your freezing breath will be slowed 50% for 2 seconds.

effects.title: Redirect
effects.text: While linked, all received damage is instead applied to your enemy.

grapple.description: Hold the button to grapple. Move your cursor to swing Grapple around. Throw your enemies into the void!

kamehameha.name: Acolyte Beam
kamehameha.description: Unleash a beam so powerful it can wipe out a full-health enemy in seconds.

effects.title: Interruptible
effects.text: If you take an enemy hit, Acolyte Beam will be interrupted.

lightning.name: Repulsor
lightning.description: Huge knockback, if your aim is good enough. Beware, the recoil from Repulsor knocks you back too.

blast.name: Acolyte Blast
blast.description: Hold down the button to charge your blast for longer. Charge for 2 seconds for maximum damage and knockback.

effects.title: Interruptible
effects.text: If you take an enemy hit, Acolyte Blast will be interrupted.

homing.description: Follows the enemy. High damage, but only if the enemy doesn't know how to dodge.

boomerang.name: Orbiter
boomerang.description: Around and around you. Keep following your enemies at orbital distance until it hits.

retractor.name: Refract
retractor.description: Refract can turn corners - hold the button down, then release the button to redirect. After it refracts, damage increases with distance travelled, so take an indirect path to do maximum damage.

backlash.name: Boomerang
backlash.description: Away and back. Hit your enemy twice, if you can. Cooldown reduced 0.75 seconds if you hit.

rocket.name: Spirit Bomb
rocket.description: You control Spirit Bomb while it is flying, but while doing this, you cannot move. Cast Spirit Bomb again to detonate at exactly the right moment.

effects.title: Interruptible
effects.text: If you take an enemy hit, Spirit Bomb will be interrupted.

effects.title: Freeze
effects.text: Enemies hit will be unable to move for a short time.

whip.name: Electroshock
whip.description: Shock your enemies at short-range. Electroshock lifesteals from your enemy.

effects.title: Fast
effects.text: Gain a 20% movement speed bonus for 3 seconds (even if you miss).

bouncer.description: The more times this bounces, the more damage this does. Get in close and keep it bouncing.

repeater.description: Every time Repeater hits, the cooldown resets and you can shoot it again immediately. Hitting the same enemy again will do 150% damage, and the third time it will do 200% damage (the maximum). Repeater takes 0.4 seconds to grow to full damage, so hit from a distance for maximum effect.

drain.description: Steal some life from your enemy. They probably didn't need it anyway.

icewall.name: Forcefield
icewall.description: Create a wall that blocks projectiles and acolytes. You can pass through your own forcefield, but other acolytes cannot, even if they are using teleport.

horcrux.name: Horcrux
horcrux.description: As long as your Horcrux is alive, you cannot die. The Horcrux will lifesteal from any nearby enemies, but will not kill them. Your Horcrux is fragile, so shoot it close to your enemy, but don't let it touch them or it will break!

saber.name: Lightsaber
saber.description: For 1 second, swing your lightsaber to deflect projectiles and knockback enemies! Saber will only last 0.25 seconds after it hits the first enemy Acolyte.

effects.title: Detach
effects.text: Lightsaber cuts through any Links or Grapples.

dualSaber.name: Dualsaber
dualSaber.description: For 1.5 seconds, swing dual lightsabers to deflect projectiles and knockback enemies! Dualsaber is slightly shorter than Lightsaber but lasts longer. Dualsaber will only last 0.25 seconds after it hits the first enemy Acolyte.

effects.title: Detach
effects.text: Dualsaber cuts through any Links or Grapples.

scourge.name: Overload
scourge.description: Release a melee-range explosion that will send your enemies flying. Be careful - this spell is so powerful it costs you some health too.

effects.title: Heavy
effects.text: Knockback reduced 75% while overloading.

shield.name: Reflect
shield.description: Reflect away projectile attacks. Ineffective against area-of-effect spells.

phaseOut.name: Phase Shift
phaseOut.description: Hold down the button to disappear from the world for up to 0.75 seconds. While phased shifted, you cannot be hurt, but you also cannot cast spells. Phase shift also cancels all knockback. Phase shift takes longer to cooldown the longer you stay in phase shift.

supernova.description: A delayed explosion to knock back your enemies. Knockback is higher at the center of the blast.

halo.name: Halo
halo.description: Build up to 3 halos over 3 seconds, then touch your enemy for lifesteal.

effects.title: Fast
effects.text: Gain a 20% movement speed boost.

effects.title: Interruptible
effects.text: The halos and speed boost will be cancelled if you are hit, or if you cast another spell.

mines.name: Energy Mines
mines.description: Mark out your territory with some Energy Mines. If you walk away from the mines, they expire. Energy mines only do damage after 0.1 seconds.

iceBomb.name: Frostsplatter
iceBomb.description: Shoot a splatter of frost in a wide arc. Pushes away objects and freezes enemies.

effects.title: Freeze
effects.text: Freeze nearby enemies for 1.25 seconds.

teleport.description: Teleport to a nearby location. Get close, or get away.

effects.title: Weak
effects.text: For 0.25 seconds after teleporting, you will only deal 25% damage and cannot deal fatal damage.

effects.title: Cleanse
effects.text: Clears all positive and negative effects.

effects.title: Void recharge
effects.text: Cools down 2x faster when in the void.

thrust.name: Charge
thrust.description: Accelerate quickly, knocking away anything in your path.

effects.title: Cleanse
effects.text: Clears all positive and negative effects.

effects.title: Void recharge
effects.text: Cools down 2x faster when in the void.

blaze.name: Blaze
blaze.description: Dash a short distance, phasing through obstacles and burning through anyone in your path.

swap.name: Swap
swap.description: Swap positions with an enemy, obstacle or meteor. Teleports if you miss.

effects.title: Cleanse
effects.text: Clears all positive and negative effects.

effects.title: Void recharge
effects.text: Cools down 2x faster when in the void.

voidRush.name: Void Rush
voidRush.description: For 3 seconds, increase movement speed 80%, and also become immune to damage from the void.

effects.title: Cleanse
effects.text: Clears all positive and negative effects.

effects.title: Void recharge
effects.text: Cools down 2x faster when in the void.

vanish.name: Vanish
vanish.description: Vanish from sight for 3 seconds, and also increase movement speed 80%.

effects.title: Cleanse
effects.text: Clears all positive and negative effects.

effects.title: Void recharge
effects.text: Cools down 2x faster when in the void.

armor.name: Spirit Armor
armor.description: Passive ability. Every atom in your body is imbued with inner strength.

effects.title: Resistant
effects.text: Reduce damage received by 15%. Applies to all forms of damage, including void damage.

empower.name: Apex Acolyte
empower.description: Passive ability. Your superior talents allow you to attack with increased effectiveness.

effects.title: Empowered
effects.text: Increase damage dealt by 15%.

boost.name: Arcane Agility
boost.description: Passive ability. Dodge even more effectively using your knowledge of the arcane.

effects.title: Fast
effects.text: Increase movement speed by 10%.

bump.name: Reverberate
bump.description: Passive ability. Reverberate sonic waves throughout your body. Knockback anyone you touch.

heal.startMessage: Game started. Fight over this healing pool!
